48
00:06:23.117 --> 00:06:24.852
<i>My code name is Catalyst.</i>

49
00:06:28.522 --> 00:06:30.691
<i>And right now you need</i>
<i>to know the following.</i>

50
00:06:32.326 --> 00:06:33.928
