<i>many there are of us.</i>

52
00:06:37.665 --> 00:06:40.368
<i>We all train to be a part of</i>
<i>a program called the Internship.</i>

53
00:06:41.168 --> 00:06:44.138
<i>And we were left to rot when</i>
<i>the program went down in flames</i>

54
00:06:44.238 --> 00:06:45.673
