61
00:07:04.892 --> 00:07:07.762
ANALYST: So guys.
the... the tusks on this guy.

62
00:07:07.828 --> 00:07:10.398
they actually grow from
the bottom instead of the top

63
00:07:10.497 --> 00:07:12.499
because they're from the. uh...
